<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/asp.81.e104969.figure19>
    dc:description "Figure 19. Coenosia inusitata, male. A Lateral view, B head, frontal view, C thorax, dorsal view, D abdomen, dorsal view, E hind femur, anterior surface, F fifth sternite, G cercus and surstylus, dorsal view, H cercus, surstylus and phallic complex, lateral view, I phallic complex, lateral view. Scale bar: 1 mm (A), 0.5 mm (B, D), 0.2 mm (C, F), 0.1 mm (G-I). Hind femur, setae on anterior surface - red circle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/882087" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/asp.81.e104969.figure20>
    dc:description "Figure 20. Coenosia inusitata, female. A lateral view, B head, frontal view, C ovipositor, dorsal view, D ovipositor, ventral view, E spermathecae. Scale bar: 1 mm (A), 0.5 mm (B-D), 0.1 mm (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/882088" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

